<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;"><strong><span style="color: #1f497d; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Randi Theil</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;"><strong><span style="color: #1f497d; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Kvinderådet</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;"><span style="color: #1f497d; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Niels Hemmingsensgade 10</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;"><span style="color: #1f497d; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">1153 København K</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;"><span style="color: #1f497d; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">tlf.: +45 33 12 80 87</span></p>
